  <summary date="2021-08-24T23:54:23Z" status="Introduced in House">Respect for Peace Corps Volunteers Act 

This bill allows the official seal or emblem of the Peace Corps and the name Peace Corps to be used on any death announcement, plaque, grave stone, or other grave marker of a former volunteer, officer, or employee of the Peace Corps.</summary>
